Summary: This is in reference to submitter file 16192 2009-03-23, 2008-08-03. UFO over Quezaltepec Volcano, San Salvador, El Salvador.
divs: Sighting DetailsTo the poster of this report, I was hoping you could tell what the black tower like objects are in your pictures. Are they towers? Since you said it was a volcano I thought that would be a strange place to put T.V. or radio towers unless it's a dormant volcano which obviously it is. The reason I am interested is my son took a picture not long ago and it looks very much like the black lines in your picture except we were on a airplane at 33k feet over Texas.
